        "Speaker": "克罗瑞娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_girl022_01",
        "zh_CN": "您好，分析员先生。承蒙关照。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜走到我面前，向我欠了欠身。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你好，克罗瑞娜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 76,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_22",
        "zh_CN": "好了，人也都到齐了——开宴！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 77,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "刚到庄园的那股热闹劲儿渐渐退去，姑娘们又拿起了各自的矜持。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 78,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就好像刚刚只是失态而已。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 79,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "或优雅，或大方，体贴而不失分寸，谈吐也颇有深度——至少对自家的生意和背景非常熟悉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 80,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "顿时感到乏味。只感觉这时的她们和米拉以及克罗瑞娜一样，戴着不同色彩的面具，乏善可陈。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 81,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "宴会继续推进下去，客人们三三两两聊着，有位置的限制，也没再像之前那样被大家围着说话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 82,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在这种俗套的欢宴中，就只剩下盘中美食能给我惊喜了。食材和调味的搭配或经典或巧妙，不由得多吃了些。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 83,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "贝蕾妮丝",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_Berenice_05",
        "zh_CN": "看来分析员先生对菜品很满意呢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 84,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是。很合我的口味——有些菜式是第一次见。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 85,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这算是菲洛索亚的本地菜吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 86,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_23",
        "zh_CN": "算是吉诺拉庄园的招牌。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 87,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_24",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜在吃这方面比较感兴趣，庄园的厨师算是受了罪了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 88,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_25",
        "zh_CN": "这里不行，那里不对……我感觉都差不多，但她就是能尝得出来。现在我这儿的厨师都成宝贝了，谁家都想来挖一下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 89,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看向克罗瑞娜，她迎着我的视线微微低头示意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 90,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜好像不太爱说话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 91,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_26",
        "zh_CN": "是有点怕生，熟悉了就好了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 92,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_27",
        "zh_CN": "对了——贝姬，你上次订的衣服已经到了，在管家那儿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 93,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "贝蕾妮丝眨了眨眼睛，看了看米拉，又看了看我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 94,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "贝蕾妮丝",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_Berenice_06",
        "zh_CN": "我刚好想问你呢。那太好了，我要去看看——不介意我直接拆开吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 95,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_28",
        "zh_CN": "你现在换上都没问题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 96,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "贝蕾妮丝",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_Berenice_07",
        "zh_CN": "那，失陪了，二位~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 97,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "衣服？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 98,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_29",
        "zh_CN": "哦，克罗瑞娜在服装设计方面也有些独特的想法，有几个著名的设计师对这些想法还算认可。所以朋友们有时候会过来请教一下她的意见。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 99,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她还真是博学。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 100,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米拉笑了笑，看了下周围，然后凑得更近了些。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 101,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_30",
        "zh_CN": "分析员先生，陶应该把克罗瑞娜的情况都告诉你了吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 102,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当然。有什么顾虑吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 103,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_31",
        "zh_CN": "确实有一点……小的担忧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 104,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米拉端起杯子抿了一口。虽然在跟我说话，视线却飘向了克罗瑞娜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 105,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_32",
        "zh_CN": "我姐姐去得早，克罗瑞娜算是跟着我长大的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 106,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_33",
        "zh_CN": "凡是要她做的事，没有做不好的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 107,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是好事嘛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 108,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_34",
        "zh_CN": "可唯独有一件事……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 109,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的眼里有骄傲，也有疲惫。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 110,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_35",
        "zh_CN": "治病。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 111,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "治病？不配合治疗吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 112,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_36",
        "zh_CN": "……成年病有多棘手？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 113,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_37",
        "zh_CN": "好多年了。全世界把能找到的方法都试遍了，也只有巴德尔抑制剂一种方法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 114,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对巴德尔抑制剂过敏是很罕见的病例。但我们会有办法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 115,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_38",
        "zh_CN": "不是不相信你们，只是事实摆在这里……找上你们，我也是抱着试试看的想法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 116,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_39",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜一直在从事遗传学的临床研究。她很清楚痊愈的希望有多低。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 117,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_40",
        "zh_CN": "她越释然，我越难过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 118,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_41",
        "zh_CN": "她才十八岁。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 119,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 120,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我也不知道该说什么好了。脑海里自然浮现起那双望着窗外的眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 121,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_42",
        "zh_CN": "哎，瞧我——净说些丧气话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 122,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_43",
        "zh_CN": "如果是你的话，也许会有奇迹吧？毕竟是你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 123,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（……毕竟是我？）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 124,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_44",
        "zh_CN": "好久没见了，分析员。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 125,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_45",
        "zh_CN": "还记得我吗？米拉·吉诺拉，你可以叫我米拉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 126,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从踏进大门时她说的第一句话开始，我就有种感觉——她早就认识我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 127,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我总觉得我们之前在哪见过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 128,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卫城学院是我们第一次见面吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 129,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我直视着她的眼睛。她皱着眉，挑着视线，好像要看透我内心深处最真实的想法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 130,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_46",
        "zh_CN": "当然。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 131,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她偏过头，端起杯子。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 132,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_47",
        "zh_CN": "还是强调一下，刚刚的话没有不信任世界树的意思。你和陶的成就有目共睹。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 133,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她举起杯子，微微低头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 134,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep1_mira_48",
        "zh_CN": "接下来一段时间，克罗瑞娜就拜托你了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 135,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "碰了碰杯，顺着她的目光，看向克罗瑞娜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 136,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她正听着长辈们的闲聊，被提到了就回应一两句，视线偶尔不经意地掠过我和米拉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 137,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我会试试的，米拉小姐。",
        "disable": 0
    }
